Setup instructions
    1. Copy widget script to ~/.config/awesome dir
    2. Add to your rc.lua this strings atop:
       require("mpd_state")    --> for MPD State Widget
       require("volume")       --> for Volume State Widget
    3. Add to your container mpd_state or volume widget.
       By default you have "mywibox" panel.

Links
    Awesome - http://awesome.naquadah.org/
    Lua - http://lua.org/
